```plantuml
@startuml eProsima_FIWARE-SH

actor Integration_Service
participant SystemHandle
participant NGSIV2Connector
participant Listener
participant Publisher
participant Subscriber
participant "FIWARE Context Broker" as FIWARE

Integration_Service -> SystemHandle: Initialize
SystemHandle -> NGSIV2Connector: Configure with YAML
SystemHandle -> Listener: Start Listening on port
SystemHandle -> Publisher: Create Publisher
SystemHandle -> Subscriber: Create Subscriber

activate Integration_Service

note right of Integration_Service: Publishing data flow
Integration_Service -> Publisher: Publish Data
Publisher -> NGSIV2Connector: Convert xtypes to JSON
NGSIV2Connector -> FIWARE: Send Data using NGSIv2 API

note right of FIWARE: Receiving data flow
FIWARE -> Listener: Push Notification
Listener -> NGSIV2Connector: Forward Notification
NGSIV2Connector -> Subscriber: Convert JSON to xtypes
Subscriber -> Integration_Service: Deliver Data

deactivate Integration_Service

@enduml
```